lyrics:
[verse]
In this game, everyone's seeking a place to hide
Playing PUBG, the adrenaline starts to rise
Ahmet Karal's leading the squad, ready to strike
Survival is the goal, they're in for the fight

[chorus]
Ahmet Karal, the King of PUBG, no fear
With strategy and skill, victory is near
In this battlefield, they're on a quest so true
Where every move counts, and only the strong will do
